24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在《Zero》的《想象》系列的最新一集中，阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 与首届气候小说奖获得者阿比·达雷 (Abi Daré) 一起亮相。阿比是畅销书&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;《所以我咆哮》&lt;/em&gt;的作者，该书讲述了青少年阿杜尼面对迷信、缺乏教育以及气候变化对尼日利亚农村社区的影响的故事。阿比与零一起谈论气候变化在她的故事中所扮演的角色，以及她如何看到尼日利亚在快速发展的过程中采用气候解决方案。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rshUnVbP8bZOBVMJiJjErtSW1IodMZhOIkjqJyn9OJvVGD-dfX2FZchB8uzTFuyTlbEYGN52FmJkjz2YO9_5w6Cwt1CsxrFSD1VR93xzpifMXcja4gnqRU2uHK2qq7ujJA81hGqfJdCDLb2eq-DbeXkI2sztc7c0AH5lW3gORL_HC_5_Kd3jvlY2RJaLUEBVvVhyGKxLoYJhIX16X3qL9_RpRgWMJ8fcBjohAVCgLI9pL8K-alZLVKlMVDD1w0X19pFk_sdU_GxVmfNd-5ZTndvod6QkVMmZOr5G2_j9qmX1iNQ3cPVaf5jv9PSwq5stq9DGIdvpY-IpuIU1cJR3VDYD_AkmUKChM7Mo32FdfKlIUhMOCdKFCIniHtBZFOKmcEatsjXf5ANio4GK-ydXIgQ/sbXDh3WlP3k5E0OebQwXvF1xCIK8L_xv/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="“我所看到的每一处，气候变化都在流血”阿比·达雷谈气候小说写作：想象系列 - 零"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/x1t3n3uV2tztL-TJupDEI2zoahRlTCBgetGGxjGwyRoY9xXbjCMzERy0xia_AiXYqlHFOE09jux0rBI_7k0wMIyw2A7qTrxNvoG6gsVAYM6-rrCdXeQqKJslOT25q_ADYd_G3o7x0wCMC2y5Asq5BnnLzoZDaF3M6WsJjJ_sRkuUBShsMidNsSiUexw7LH3JtqARUAWaGoZffILSJtMN9-ajBR3k16q7XqScvJGerpObh7IabAyPedX6w4aaDnPaL3yLHOKxbFBTwSB_pXKdbyPgn44IPmXi1sT0epji9ZIEtdh_JTyLib_KKe1OKu6MlUcYfg/m3jXsn0o3i_7OSp5t6effwPo1ntDyXfS/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AftGxtsDKgmv8bb5ovGPVMzqo1u-Snin_0dNnw66g54WKANyyVeAeBH7nUggXyXhPnT7c05_UdpXyu404OSJ0m1PrwLDOwOqnKEE6mzznaS7YhlJ7X70HoEYXbvUrRgRgf0umBdlgegSVxZW-W_3MpPpIPHb1B7s0Wy_QB78sKRIzPwZvEcey4OacGoZdkxnVBFkJ8tSLo4-HEcaYV3ZVLa2PXi5RMwmkHnVVFe9-a1QQCXRBtoBukzbbtgZYMJjONfZcSeLT9iC8y50xMzcv1MSuxTo631XFb2EQbTZALJW3x_GbdI__9cweeMQX402hMFFNe3lKp23_fGVZroRu68e14Cb/jy3iTeJdbe39bRqHapoc_B1VjlShKJFy/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; 